won by 16 to 6. He had earlier scored 2 tries and kicked a conversion.\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 1 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = North Shore\n| score = 33\u20130\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =North Shore v Eden\n| page = 8\n| work=[[Auckland Star]]| volume=XLIII| issue=132\n| date = 1912-06-03\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/AS19120603.2.68\n| accessdate = 2019-12-16}}</ref>\n| away = Eden\n| try1 = unknown\n| con1 = unknown\n| pen1 =\n| try2 =\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Eden Park # 3\n| attendance =\n| referee = Mr. Feilding\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 1 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 16\u20136\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Ponsonby Beat Newton\n| page = 8\n| work=[[Auckland Star]]| volume=XLIII| issue=132\n| date = 1912-06-03\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/AS19120603.2.68\n| accessdate = 2019-12-16}}</ref>\n| away = Newton\n| try1 = [[Charles Dunning]] 2, [[Charles Savory]] 2\n| con1 = [[Arthur Carlaw]], [[Charles Savory]]\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = [[Arthur Francis (rugby)|Arthur Francis]] 2\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Eden Park\n| attendance =\n| referee = Mr. Cunningham\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 1 June\n| time =\n| home = City\n| score = 5\u20133\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Manukau V City/Close Call For City\n| page = 8\n| work=[[Auckland Star]]| volume=XLIII| issue=132\n| date = 1912-06-03\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/AS19120603.2.68\n| accessdate = 2019-12-16}}</ref>\n| away = Manukau\n| try1 = Frederick Mansell\n| con1 =\n| pen1 = Fredicrick Mansell\n| try2 = [[Jim Rukutai]]\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Eden Park\n| attendance =\n| referee = Mr Roy Oliphant\n}}\n\n======Round 5======\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 8 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = North Shore\n| score = 6\u201313\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Ponsonby Beat North Shore\n| page = 8\n| work=[[Auckland Star]]| volume=XLIII| issue