(R4), Manukau try v North Shore (R3), Newton try v Manukau (R5), Newton 2 tries v Manukau (R10), Eden 25 points v City (R10), City 5 points v Eden (R10). This amounts to 84 points unattributed out of 773 points scored in total.\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n \n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible sortable\" style=\"text-align:left; font-size:100%; width:80%;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"100%\" | Top try scorers\n|-\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | Rank\n! style=\"width:35%;\" | Player\n! style=\"width:35%;\" | Team\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | Tries\n<!-- Pos                           || Player         || Team        || Tries-->\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1 ||D Healy||Newton Rangers|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |7\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1 ||W Tobin||Newton Rangers|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |7\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1 ||[[Charles Savory]]||Ponsonby United|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |7\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4 ||Alan Blakey||Newton Rangers|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |5\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4 ||C Brockliss||Newton Rangers|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |5\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4 ||Bush||Newton Rangers|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |5\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4 ||[[Billy Dervan]]||Newton Rangers|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |5\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4 ||[[Charles Dunning]]||Ponsonby United|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |5\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4 ||Mincham||Ponsonby United|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |5\n|-\n|   style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4 ||George Hunt||City Rovers|| style=\"text-align:center;\" |5\n|}\n \n{{col-2}}\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible sortable\" style=\"text-align:left; font-size:100%; width:80%;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"100%\" | Top point scorers\n|-\n! style=\"width:15%;\" | Rank\n! style=\"width:30%;\" | Player\n! style=\"width:30%;\" | Team\n! style=\"width:25%;\" | Points\n<!-- Pos                           